WEBVTT

00:17.476 --> 00:21.855
<i>The water renews
but does not shed its layers. No.</i>

00:27.402 --> 00:29.947
<i>It drags buried memories to the present.</i>

00:35.285 --> 00:37.079
<i>Once, below these waters,</i>

00:38.413 --> 00:43.001
<i>giant predators swam. Mythical.</i>

00:45.712 --> 00:48.382
<i>Those predators grew legs
and made it to land.</i>

00:49.508 --> 00:52.219
<i>If they could do that,
would it be so surprising if once,</i>

00:52.219 --> 00:57.558
<i>upon one of these times,
witches had been here too?</i>

00:59.852 --> 01:04.022
<i>Each tale told upon this water
informs the next story...</i>

01:05.440 --> 01:06.692
<i>and the next.</i>

02:20.766 --> 02:22.768
Don't know why I had to come out here.

02:24.061 --> 02:26.522
Man agrees to pay you $70,000 for a book,

02:27.105 --> 02:29.441
you best believe you deliver
that shit to him personally.

02:30.943 --> 02:35.030
You know what we look like?
Two drug dealers out to make a sale.

02:36.573 --> 02:38.075
Drug dealers don't gift wrap.

02:41.119 --> 02:42.621
Yeah. I think we should make that...

02:43.622 --> 02:45.332
- Here you go.
- Thanks.

02:45.332 --> 02:46.416
Yeah. No problem.

02:50.128 --> 02:51.213
Here you go.

02:52.798 --> 02:54.174
- Hey.
- Hey.

02:55.551 --> 02:57.177
You got another meeting tonight?

02:58.178 --> 02:59.179
What?

02:59.179 --> 03:02.015
The Survivors Club at the
Chinese Community Center in Flushing.

03:03.141 --> 03:04.142
You been stalking me?

03:05.143 --> 03:08.188
It popped up on the
tribute page when you checked in online.

03:08.772 --> 03:11.316
