What are you talking about?

03:11.316 --> 03:12.401
Tribute page.

03:14.361 --> 03:15.362
For Brian.

03:21.159 --> 03:22.953
"Tribute to Brian."

03:24.204 --> 03:25.414
I'm a fan.

03:25.414 --> 03:28.625
Not a fan, but, you know what I mean.

03:29.251 --> 03:30.836
<i>May angels watch over
that poor child...</i>

03:30.836 --> 03:31.753
<i>Rest in piss.</i>

03:31.753 --> 03:33.338
<i>Two working parents cannot raise a child.</i>

03:33.338 --> 03:35.215
- <i>Genetically unfit.</i>
- <i>Postpartem.</i>

03:35.215 --> 03:36.300
<i>Apollo killed them both...</i>

03:36.300 --> 03:39.887
<i>Dinner plans tonight.
A meal inspired by baby Brian.</i>

03:39.887 --> 03:41.180
<i>Boiled vegetables.</i>

03:41.763 --> 03:44.975
"Boiled vegetables."
Who the hell are these people, man?

03:46.977 --> 03:47.978
Like, what--

03:49.188 --> 03:51.106
Why would this guy make this?

03:51.106 --> 03:52.357
I thought you knew.

03:53.066 --> 03:54.610
My man, I never w--

03:55.110 --> 03:56.820
When I went there,
I saw that you checked in

03:56.820 --> 03:58.488
with The Survivors.
I figured that meant you knew.

03:58.488 --> 04:01.783
No. I checked in
so if my parole officer logged on,

04:01.783 --> 04:02.993
that I'd be able to cover my ass,

04:02.993 --> 04:04.912
but I didn't know it was gonna
end up on this.

04:04.912 --> 04:07.164
Wow. Here I am tripping on witches,

04:07.164 --> 04:10.417
