conjuring up something way worse.

04:11.376 --> 04:12.669
What you say?

04:12.669 --> 04:14.963
Nothing, man. I'm not talking to you.

04:21.220 --> 04:22.137
Is that our guy?

04:24.348 --> 04:28.352
Wow. Beige on beige. Tan man.
Very fashionable.

04:29.436 --> 04:31.647
Who the fuck still drinks Tab?

04:32.940 --> 04:36.360
Okay, this is a man who has not been
with a woman in a very long time.

04:36.360 --> 04:39.363
In years. Decades.

04:39.363 --> 04:42.699
One of these incel fat fucks
always posting heinous shit online

04:42.699 --> 04:44.451
about how no one appreciates
how special he is

04:44.451 --> 04:47.788
- and how women only want jerks.
- All right. Calm down.

04:47.788 --> 04:50.666
This is the guy that's gonna
give us a five-figure check, all right?

04:50.666 --> 04:51.583
But keep it up.

04:54.461 --> 04:57.464
I was wrong.
This guy's never been with a woman.

04:58.298 --> 05:00.551
