what else he's probably never done?

05:03.428 --> 05:06.557
He's probably never
joined a Baby Brian fan page.

05:08.058 --> 05:09.101
- Hey.
- Apollo.

05:11.770 --> 05:12.771
Hey, William.

05:12.771 --> 05:14.231
Don't trip. He seems safe.

05:14.231 --> 05:16.525
Hey. Good to see you.
Lemme take you to my office.

05:18.068 --> 05:20.779
Sorry. It's a bit of a mess.

05:20.779 --> 05:21.947
It's all right.

05:22.823 --> 05:23.824
Here. Let me--

05:26.159 --> 05:27.160
That's cute.

05:27.160 --> 05:30.038
Oh, yeah. Those are from my daughters.

05:31.290 --> 05:32.624
See, he's got daughters.

05:33.667 --> 05:34.877
And one wife.

05:36.879 --> 05:39.131
I used to call them
my little strawberries.

05:40.507 --> 05:44.011
When they'd get mad,
their faces would get so red.

05:47.139 --> 05:48.348
Got that from me.

06:09.328 --> 06:10.913
