06:30.557 --> 06:32.059
Here she is.

06:35.521 --> 06:36.855
Guys, come on.

06:37.439 --> 06:38.440
Yeah.

06:47.241 --> 06:48.784
You know, I can't swim.

06:48.784 --> 06:51.703
- Guys, come down.
- I'll just grab here. Okay.

06:55.207 --> 06:56.416
I got beer.

07:00.045 --> 07:02.798
