08:07.487 --> 08:10.073
You know, I guess I hoped
to see it before I bought it.

08:11.533 --> 08:13.035
- You wanna--
- That's okay.

08:13.952 --> 08:15.120
You know, I trust you guys.

08:15.120 --> 08:18.290
Here. Give it to me. Here.

08:19.124 --> 08:20.501
It's-- I'll do it for you.

08:20.501 --> 08:21.668
