09:57.514 --> 09:58.849
And I know what matters now.

10:01.351 --> 10:03.520
I know I could do better if she came back.

10:05.272 --> 10:10.694
And I love my daughters so much,
and I never said it.

10:11.987 --> 10:12.988
No, I never said it.

10:13.572 --> 10:15.324
And people need to hear the words,
you know?

10:16.909 --> 10:17.910
Yes.

10:19.703 --> 10:23.624
