just to try and win her back with this.

10:24.958 --> 10:27.669
I mean, what's your feeling, guys?
Could it work?

10:29.087 --> 10:31.298
- I--
- Yeah, tell her whatever you told us, man.

10:31.298 --> 10:34.301
- I'm gonna wrap it back up for you.
- Tell her that. Okay?

10:35.511 --> 10:36.470
There you go.

10:36.470 --> 10:38.138
I sent the funds electronically.

10:39.640 --> 10:41.975
Yes. Yeah, that'll work.

10:42.893 --> 10:44.061
That's it, then.

10:48.232 --> 10:52.945
You know, if this doesn't get Gretta back,
I'm all tapped out.

10:55.739 --> 10:59.785
And this paper, it really is a nice touch.

11:06.458 --> 11:07.626
Patrice!

11:22.933 --> 11:24.268
It's all right.

12:04.558 --> 12:05.601
God!

12:10.522 --> 12:11.857
Emma!

13:31.979 --> 13:33.230
Hey.

13:34.982 --> 13:38.569
Thanks for coming to meet me here.

13:42.155 --> 13:43.866
This place has good memories.

13:45.200 --> 13:47.786
And Emma, she was addicted
to those dumplings,

13:48.662 --> 13:49.955
her whole pregnancy.

13:54.710 --> 13:56.420
I wanna thank you too for--

13:58.130 --> 14:00.090
Helping my mom
with the funeral arrangements.

14:00.841 --> 14:02.718
Brian was my nephew.

14:08.724 --> 14:11.476
