on his grave every week?

14:12.019 --> 14:13.103
We paid extra for that.

14:14.771 --> 14:16.815
I haven't been going. So...

14:16.815 --> 14:18.942
- But you have to--
- I wanted to...

14:21.069 --> 14:23.864
pay you back for what you've done.

14:25.199 --> 14:27.492
What's it? About $10,000 for a birth?

14:27.492 --> 14:28.785
What are you...

14:32.915 --> 14:34.416
