14:40.130 --> 14:42.966
Yeah, well, you trained us.

14:47.721 --> 14:48.555
Apollo...

14:48.555 --> 14:53.018
I never even got to hear her third wish.

14:54.102 --> 14:57.314
It could've been anything, you know?
She could've--

14:58.023 --> 14:59.608
She could've just told--

15:01.151 --> 15:02.736
I think you should know...

15:09.993 --> 15:11.995
it wasn't supposed to be like this.

15:14.665 --> 15:15.874
This is what it is.

15:51.451 --> 15:53.203
Goodbye, Valentines.

15:58.750 --> 15:59.751
Thank you.

16:19.688 --> 16:21.523
What the fuck? What?

16:42.044 --> 16:43.045
What?

17:06.234 --> 17:07.069
Fuck you!

17:24.461 --> 17:25.628
What?

17:29.341 --> 17:31.176
Where the fuck are you?

17:37.182 --> 17:38.392
William.

17:39.852 --> 17:42.354
Hey! William!

17:43.438 --> 17:44.773
Goddamn it.

17:46.066 --> 17:49.903
- William! Where the fuck are you? Hey!
- Hey. Hey, Mr. Kagwa--

17:49.903 --> 17:51.446
- You little fucking shit!
- Apollo!

17:51.446 --> 17:52.823
Sorry to see you again like this-- No.

17:52.823 --> 17:54.658
- Hey! Oh, come on man.
- The fuck do you think this is?

17:54.658 --> 17:57.327
- This a fucking sick joke to you? Huh?
- No. No.

17:57.911 --> 17:59.746
I didn't mean to get all cloak
and dagger about it. Come on.

17:59.746 --> 18:01.915
What the fuck are you talking about?
Do you know Emma's alive?

18:01.915 --> 18:03.792
- Yes, I do. I swear-- Look--
- What? How?

18:03.792 --> 18:06.253
- I only just found out.
- What the fuck do you mean?

18:06.253 --> 18:08.922
The NYPD
and the fucking Feds couldn't find her,

18:08.922 --> 18:11.508
and you mean to tell me you did?
Is that what you're telling me?

18:11.508 --> 18:13.802
Look, there was a time
when government agencies like that

18:13.802 --> 18:15.637
were the only resource
a person had, Apollo.

18:15.637 --> 18:18.473
- Shut the fuck up with that shit!
- That's not true anymore.

18:19.975 --> 18:23.145
You know, a hundred people with
a hundred computers across the country,

18:23.687 --> 18:25.606
they can cover as much ground as them.

18:25.606 --> 18:26.899
They can cover more.

18:28.025 --> 18:31.069
And if those people really care,
they'll work day and night.

18:31.069 --> 18:32.154
