18:32.905 --> 18:35.574
And that's just what they did
when I told them I wanted to help you.

18:35.574 --> 18:39.161
Okay, okay. So where is she?

18:39.161 --> 18:42.372
If what you say is true,
where is Emma Valentine?

18:43.248 --> 18:44.958
She's on an island in the East River.

18:47.377 --> 18:50.797
- I'm serious. I swear it.
- This fucking guy.

18:51.423 --> 18:52.674
I'm serious.

18:54.176 --> 18:56.261
The Wise Ones, Apollo. I found 'em.

18:57.304 --> 18:58.347
Who are you?

18:59.223 --> 19:02.017
- Apollo, I'm your friend.
- Don't! You're not my fucking friend.

19:02.017 --> 19:03.602
Stop saying that. Stop touching me.

19:05.312 --> 19:06.563
How do I get to her?

