19:49.815 --> 19:50.899
Okay.

19:51.775 --> 19:53.735
Good news is I did my due diligence

19:53.735 --> 19:56.113
- on Wheeler before you got here.
- And?

19:56.113 --> 19:59.199
William Webster Wheeler.
Gotta love alliteration.

19:59.700 --> 20:00.742
Born in Levittown.

20:00.742 --> 20:03.871
Owns a house in Forest Hills,
on 86th street.

20:03.871 --> 20:07.082
Served in the Air Force as a programming
specialist in the early '80s.

20:07.082 --> 20:11.003
After that, worked for
the Medical University of South Carolina.

20:11.003 --> 20:15.674
Started making his way back northeast.
Been working as an app developer.

20:16.550 --> 20:17.593
Damn.

20:18.260 --> 20:20.429
- This guy is who he says he is.
- Yeah.

20:20.429 --> 20:22.764
- That means something these days.
- Yeah, he's gonna get a

20:22.764 --> 20:24.224
boat tomorrow night...

20:24.975 --> 20:27.019
Yeah, so why is this guy helping you?

20:27.019 --> 20:29.104
- I mean, what's in it for him?
- I don't know.

20:29.104 --> 20:30.147
Maybe he's fucking crazy.

20:30.147 --> 20:32.733
Maybe he wants to throw me off the boat.
I really don't care.

20:37.905 --> 20:38.947
Yeah.

20:44.745 --> 20:47.414
This looks like CCTV camera footage.

20:47.414 --> 20:50.209
