some serious digging.

20:55.130 --> 20:58.592
<i>What is a ghost?
The spirit of a dead person,</i>

20:58.592 --> 21:00.093
<i>or a vision seen askew?</i>

21:02.554 --> 21:05.349
<i>Three months since he'd last
seen her alive,</i>

21:05.349 --> 21:08.685
