to show us support,

22:47.034 --> 22:48.869
but I'm actually out here with you.

22:50.412 --> 22:52.039
Look, we need to be careful.

22:52.039 --> 22:55.083
Vampires can't come into your house
unless you invite them, Apollo.

22:55.876 --> 22:59.588
