leaving your front door wide open

23:00.547 --> 23:03.509
and telling any creature
of the night they can just come right in.

23:11.975 --> 23:13.602
Wow. Rikers.

23:14.269 --> 23:15.437
Lights out.

23:49.096 --> 23:50.472
How would you do it?

23:50.472 --> 23:51.765
Jump off George Washington Bridge.

24:05.112 --> 24:06.113
Shit.

24:36.351 --> 24:39.605
<i>Would you even know if you
crossed into a fairy tale?</i>

24:41.607 --> 24:43.567
<i>Slipped between the pages of a book?</i>

24:48.572 --> 24:53.911
<i>There are portals in this world that we
may never know we've trespassed through.</i>

25:17.267 --> 25:20.812
There. Look, right there. There it is.

25:21.855 --> 25:24.274
Oh, my gosh. You found it.

25:26.818 --> 25:27.819
Yeah, I'm gonna beach us.

25:28.779 --> 25:29.947
Okay.

25:48.215 --> 25:49.216
Ready?

25:49.842 --> 25:50.843
Yes.

26:01.478 --> 26:02.479
